6.) Ethereal Rune/Arcane Rune ---- Two hits tops and it's down
<br />
7.) An animation. ---- you have GOT to be kidding me.
<br />
8.) Mem blur/Enhanced Forgetfullness ---- Usually do squat to save you once you got agro. 
<br />

<br />
A 6k rune on bards who can already do all of our jobs - only better and while running / tanking - is simply... a slap in our faces.
<br />

<br />
Rather than focusing on which button to push when a mob hits me because I tried to mez it and had to discover it's unmezzable (with this spell), I'd rather be focusing on which mob out of the 5 parked ones I need to deal with next.
<br />

<br />
I don't want to have to worry whether a certain ability is going to be up when the next mob mashes me into the side of a hill. That's not my job.
<br />

<br />
Parking that mob to be dealt with as and when my group sees fit - that IS my job, and I'm currently limited or even prohibited as to where I can do that.
<br />

<br />
And what's with the (with this spell) rubbish? I hear the top mez gets that as well on some mobs... so... what gives? This is *after* the mez hits and the thing (and it's friends) is on you like flies on $hit.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
